In this article, Vice President Mike Pence welcomes members of the Cabinet, Congress, business leaders, and three American astronauts to the White House. He praises President Donald Trump's vision for American leadership in space and announces that the President will take action to bring a renewed sense of purpose to America's space policy. Pence believes that this action will strengthen the economy, unlock new opportunities and technologies, inspire children to pursue education in STEM fields, enhance national defense, and strengthen the American spirit. Pence concludes by introducing President Trump, who will speak about his vision for American leadership in space.